citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1100am on
08/01/2016.
Inspectors spoke with licensee and licensee stated that she was out of town.
Additional Inspectors
Tygart Michael, Supervisory Animal Care Specialist
